definitions.definition: The sixth letter of the modern Greek alphabet ( Ζ ( Z ) , ζ ( z ) ) preceded by epsilon ( Ε ( E ) , ε ( e ) ) and followed by eta , ( Η ( I ) , η ( i ) ); or the seventh letter in the ancient Greek alphabet, in which it is preceded by digamma ( Ϝ ( W ) , ϝ ( w ) )
